casebody.data:
Raymond LAYTON, Appellant(s)/Petitioner(s),
v.
DITECH FINANCIAL LLC, etc., Appellee(s)/Respondent(s), CASE NO.: 3D17-0713 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Third District. SEPTEMBER 20, 2017 LAGOA, SCALES and LUCK, JJ., concur.

ORDERED that appellee's motion to dismiss appeal is granted, and this appeal from the Circuit Court for Miami-Dade County, Florida is hereby dismissed.
